Get Nasdaq tickers

nasdaq_tickers.Rd

This gets all Nasdaq ticker symbols from the Nasdaq website.

nasdaq_tickers(exchange = "nasdaq")

Arguments

exchange

exchange ("nasdaq" or "nyse")

Value

data frame

Examples

nasdaq_tickers()
